{"view":"article","slug":"sq-intermediate-lars","category":"CHS","subcategory":null,"topDir":"CHS","title":{"zh":"SQ1进阶拉尔斯法"},"content":{"zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image1.emf\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>SQ1进阶拉尔斯法</strong></p><p>扇贝风筝公式, 含扰动的公式 *. n = n0; n = 0n; U = 3; D = 3; M2 = 1/-1-1/01.</p><p>情况名称: x = 4个灯, J = 1个灯, N = 无灯, A = 相邻, I = 相对, U = 三循环. </p><p><strong>CS (复形) [48]</strong></p><p>先转化成下面这些形，再做公式变成方形-方形. 理解记忆. </p><p><strong>二或三步形</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>/33/</p></td><td><p>/3/</p></td><td><p>/-1/-3/</p></td><td><p>/2/3/</p></td><td><p>/-3/-3/</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>/-1-2/-3/</p></td><td><p>/12/-3-3/</p></td><td><p>/1/-3-3/</p></td><td><p>/-2/33/</p></td><td><p>/-14/-3/</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>S (Stars星)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>/24/-2-1/33/</p></td><td><p>/22/0-1/33/</p></td><td><p>/-4-2/-14/-3/</p></td><td><p>/4/12/3-2/21/03/</p></td><td><p>/2/12/3-2/21/03/</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>5S (5 Stars五星)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"5\"></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>/04/12/-3-3/</p></td><td><p>/0-2/-1-2/-3-3/</p></td><td><p>/02/12/-3-3/</p></td><td><p>/-2/01/33/</p></td><td><p>/-4/-14/-3/</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-la