><td colspan=\"12\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"12\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"12\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"12\"><p><strong>四步形</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image90.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image92.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image94.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image96.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image98.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>/23/12/3/-11</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p>/-2-3/-1-2/-3/</p></td><td colspan=\"4\"><p>/-2/-1/-3/</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p>/01/0-1/-3/-11</p></td><td><p>/3/-1-2/0-3/</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>CO (角翻) [8]</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>31 <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image100.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/70</p></td><td><p>13 <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image102.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/70</p></td><td><p> II <strong><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image104.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong>16/70</p></td><td><p>DD <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image106.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/70</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>1/U/-1 or -2-3/U'/-1</p><p>43/D'/-1 or -56/D/-1</p></td><td><p>1/U2'D'/-1 or -2-3/U2'D/-1</p><p>43/UD2/-1 or -56/U'D2/-1</p></td><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529125182\"></a>1/-1  </p></td><td><p>1/UD/-1</p><p>-23/U'D'/-1 </p></td></tr><tr><td><p>ID <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image108.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">8/70</p></td><td><p>DI<img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image110.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">8/70</p></td><td><p>44<img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image112.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/70</p></td><td><p>    <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image114.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/70</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>1/D/D/-1</p><p>13/D'/D'/-1</p></td><td><p>1/U'/U'/-1</p><p>-2/U/U/-1</p></td><td><p>1/U2'D2'/-1</p></td><td><p>Solved </p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><a id=\"_Hlk529275049\"></a></p><p><strong>EO (棱翻) [8]</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>11 <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image116.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/70</p></td><td><p>LL <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image118.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/70</p></td><td><p>II <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image120.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/70</p></td><td><p>44 <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image122.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/70</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529112214\"></a>1/U/U/-1-1/-21/U'/-1</p></td><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529122247\"></a>1<a id=\"_Hlk530072763\"></a>/U/-1-1/U'/01</p><p>43/U'/-1-1/41/</p></td><td><p>M2</p></td><td><p>1/-1-1/-24/-1-1/01</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>IL <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image124.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">8/70</p></td><td><p>LI <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image126.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">8/70</p></td><td><p>33 <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image128.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/70</p></td><td><p>    <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image130.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/70</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529112818\"></a>0-1/U/U'/11/U/U'/-1</p></td><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529112844\"></a><a id=\"_Hlk529122407\"></a>1/U/U/-1-1/-21/-4-1/01</p></td><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529112514\"></a>1/U/U/-1-1/U'/U'/01</p></td><td><p>Solved</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>EO阶段预判CP:</strong> 所有EO公式都不改变CP.</p><p><strong>CP (角序) [8]</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p> JJ <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image132.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">16/36</p></td><td><p>NN <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image134.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/36</p></td><td><p>Jx <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image136.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/36</p></td><td><p>xJ <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image138.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/36</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk529122814\"></a><a id=\"_Hlk530072802\"></a>/U'/UD/D'/</p></td><td><p>/UD'/U'D/</p></td><td><p>/UD'/U/U'/D/U'/ </p></td><td><p>/UD'/D/U'/U/U'/</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>JN <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image140.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/36</p></td><td><p>NJ <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image142.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">4/36</p></td><td><p>Nx <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image144.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/36</p></td><td><p>xN <img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image146.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">1/36</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk9889758\"></a>/D'/D/D'/D/</p></td><td><p><a id=\"_Hlk9889790\"></a>/U'/U/U'/U/</p></td><td><p>/U/U'/D/D/U'/U/</p></td><td><p>/D'/D/U'/U'/D/D'/</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>CP阶段控制EP: </strong>在CP公式前加入预设，会使EP变得简单. 根据上下层是否存在左棒来选择预操作. </p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p>U</p><p>D</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq-intermediate-lars/zh/image150.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p><img src=\"/stats/alg/media/sq